### ===========================================
### Pathfinder 2e AI Oracle - API Requests
### ===========================================
### Prerequisite: make run-local
### OpenAPI spec: http://localhost:8080/openapi.yaml
### ===========================================

### ----------- Import API -----------

### Import all categories from GitHub
### Only downloads files that are new or have changed (SHA comparison)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/import/all

### Get available import categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/import/categories

### Get import statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/import/stats

### Get all import jobs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/import/jobs

### Get specific job status (replace {jobId} with actual UUID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/import/jobs/{{jobId}}

### ----------- Ingestion API -----------
### (Vectorization for RAG - async with job tracking)

### Ingest entries into vector store (incremental - only new/changed)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ingestion/all

### Ingest all entries (full re-index)
### Warning: May take 15-30 minutes with Ollama embeddings
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ingestion/all?force=true

### Get all ingestion jobs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ingestion/jobs

### Get specific ingestion job status (replace {jobId} with actual UUID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ingestion/jobs/{{jobId}}

### Get available types with counts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ingestion/types

### Get ingestion statistics (total, vectorized, pending)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ingestion/stats


